WEBVTT

00:07.560 --> 00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:36.840 --> 01:42.360
‎ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>‎QUEEN CHU</i>‎ ON QIDIAN.COM

01:47.800 --> 01:50.160
THE FIRST YEAR OF TIANSHU

01:51.560 --> 01:54.440
<i>The late Emperor, Xiao Jing,</i>
<i>and I were close from our youth.</i>

01:54.520 --> 01:58.640
<i>I once believed</i>
<i>we would be lifelong friends.</i>

01:58.720 --> 02:00.840
<i>Xiao Jing swore to become a wise ruler,</i>

02:01.520 --> 02:04.520
<i>so I promised to defend the state for him.</i>

02:04.600 --> 02:07.040
<i>The Northern Desert</i>
<i>gathered 50,000 cavalry,</i>

02:07.120 --> 02:09.440
<i>and the commander of Yunzhong</i>
<i>requested reinforcements.</i>

02:11.000 --> 02:12.160
I'll go.

02:14.080 --> 02:16.560
-What did you say?
-Yunzhong is a vital frontier stronghold

02:17.080 --> 02:17.920
that we cannot afford to lose.

02:18.880 --> 02:20.440
But how can I send you

02:20.520 --> 02:22.440
to the most dangerous place
just as I ascend the throne?

02:22.520 --> 02:24.120
You need a victory all the more

02:24.200 --> 02:26.280
as the new emperor.

02:32.000 --> 02:34.640
Chu Ling is hereby appointed Guard General

02:34.720 --> 02:37.840
to command the frontier troops and shall
proceed to Yunzhong Prefecture today.

02:39.040 --> 02:39.880
<i>That day,</i>

02:40.720 --> 02:42.640
<i>he handed me</i>
<i>the Sword of the Loong's Roar,</i>

02:42.720 --> 02:43.880
<i>the symbol of power.</i>

02:44.480 --> 02:47.960
<i>Yet even the sharpest blade</i>
<i>cannot sever what is destined.</i>

02:48.480 --> 02:50.880
<i>In my very first battle</i>
<i>upon entering Yunzhong,</i>

02:50.960 --> 02:52.520
<i>I met her.</i>

02:53.040 --> 02:56.760
Greenhorn from the South,
do you dare to face me in battle?

03:06.920 --> 03:10.000
<i>General of the Northern Desert,</i>
<i>Alan Ruoying.</i>

03:10.840 --> 03:15.800
<i>Later, I saw her on a barren hill,</i>
<i>weeping for her fallen soldiers.</i>

03:15.880 --> 03:17.120
<i>Only then did I realize</i>

03:17.200 --> 03:18.920
<i>that the fierce Rakshasa</i>
<i>of the Northern Desert</i>

03:19.000 --> 03:21.360
<i>revealed a heart beyond slaughter.</i>

03:21.440 --> 03:24.640
General Chu, walking alone at night
without your guards?

03:24.720 --> 03:26.960
Aren't you afraid I'll take your head
to feed my war banner?

03:27.640 --> 03:31.000
I did not come here to argue with you.

03:31.080 --> 03:34.240
I wanted to talk to you.

03:34.320 --> 03:37.720
What is there for us to talk about?

03:41.320 --> 03:43.880
-Peace.
-Peace?

03:46.520 --> 03:47.960
<i>I went alone to see her</i>

03:48.760 --> 03:50.880
<i>and gave her the jade pendant</i>
<i>my mother had left me,</i>

03:50.960 --> 03:53.600
<i>engraved with the word "Peace".</i>

03:54.120 --> 03:57.080
<i>After some hesitation,</i>
<i>she finally accepted it</i>

03:57.160 --> 03:59.440
<i>and gave me a bone whistle</i>
<i>from the Northern Desert in return.</i>

04:00.120 --> 04:02.480
<i>She said she was willing</i>
<i>to risk everything to try.</i>

04:04.400 --> 04:06.560
<i>However, her efforts to plead peace</i>
<i>with the jade pendant</i>

04:06.640 --> 04:07.680
<i>only led to the Northern Desert King</i>

04:07.760 --> 04:09.960
<i>ordering her execution</i>
<i>in front of both armies.</i>

04:11.000 --> 04:13.080
<i>I had no choice but to bring her back</i>
<i>to the State of Chu.</i>

04:13.600 --> 04:17.079
<i>I told her that if the eagle of the desert</i>
<i>loses its way,</i>

04:17.880 --> 04:19.959
<i>let it be a flower still in bloom.</i>

04:20.800 --> 04:24.160
<i>From then on,</i>
<i>there was no longer Alan Ruoying,</i>

04:24.240 --> 04:27.240
<i>only my wife, Mu Mianhong.</i>

04:38.640 --> 04:40.880
<i>Then the imperial decree</i>
<i>arrived from the Capital.</i>

04:40.960 --> 04:42.080
<i>His Majesty</i>

04:42.800 --> 04:45.120
<i>demanded that I break my own oath,</i>

04:46.240 --> 04:48.920
<i>saying that executing the mother</i>
<i>while sparing the child</i>

04:49.000 --> 04:50.960
<i>was for my future</i>

04:51.040 --> 04:54.120
<i>and for the sake of my clan.</i>

04:59.600 --> 05:01.080
What are you doing?

05:14.080 --> 05:17.000
I requested to guard Yunzhong Prefecture
for the rest of my days.

05:17.600 --> 05:18.640
Without an imperial decree,

05:19.840 --> 05:21.960
<i>I shall never cross</i>
<i>into the Capital again.</i>

05:25.440 --> 05:27.240
<i>At that moment, I finally understood</i>

05:27.320 --> 05:28.880
<i>that even the sharpest sword</i>

05:28.960 --> 05:30.760
<i>cannot pierce the calculations</i>
<i>of an emperor.</i>

05:31.520 --> 05:35.080
<i>Powerless, I hid her away</i>
<i>in Cangmu Stronghold,</i>

05:35.160 --> 05:37.880
<i>under the guise of suppressing bandits.</i>

05:39.960 --> 05:40.800
Deliver the victory report!

05:42.960 --> 05:44.520
The bandit leader, Mu Mianhong,

05:45.760 --> 05:47.240
leaped from the cliff

05:48.000 --> 05:49.680
to her death!

05:51.720 --> 05:54.160
To honor His Majesty's grace!

05:56.200 --> 05:59.200
<i>On the day you were born,</i>
<i>she whispered your name.</i>

06:00.240 --> 06:01.280
<i>She said…</i>

06:01.360 --> 06:03.120
I hope that by the time you grow up,

06:03.920 --> 06:06.200
there would be no more wars

06:06.800 --> 06:11.560
and you would be able
to see the sun rise every day.

06:12.320 --> 06:14.360
Like the rising morning sun,

06:17.920 --> 06:22.040
you should be named Chu Zhao,
as the rising sun.

06:23.080 --> 06:24.200
Zhao.

06:25.200 --> 06:27.320
You must grow up without a care.

06:28.080 --> 06:30.720
If anyone asks about your mother,

06:31.640 --> 06:32.920
tell them

06:34.160 --> 06:35.400
she lives

06:36.720 --> 06:38.400
in the Capital

06:39.400 --> 06:41.240
and is skilled

06:42.240 --> 06:43.880
in all the refined arts.

06:45.000 --> 06:47.360
Although she cannot watch you grow up,

06:48.160 --> 06:49.760
she loves you

06:49.840 --> 06:51.520
JOY AND HEALTH FOREVER

06:52.120 --> 06:53.880
more than anyone else.

06:57.400 --> 06:58.360
Zhao.

07:01.360 --> 07:03.240
This is the answer you wanted.

07:04.440 --> 07:06.280
What nonsense are you talking about?

07:07.400 --> 07:09.640
Where did you hear such a story?

07:12.080 --> 07:13.360
It is not exciting at all.

07:14.920 --> 07:16.080
Do not tell it ever again.

07:16.760 --> 07:18.480
I am not lying.

07:18.560 --> 07:20.400
My mother was a noble lady
from the Capital,

07:21.240 --> 07:22.520
a well-bred daughter of a prominent house,

07:22.600 --> 07:23.960
not some general from the Northern Desert.

07:31.880 --> 07:35.280
My father said you are my mother. Are you?

07:37.960 --> 07:39.040
Father,

07:39.120 --> 07:42.280
are all the stories you told me
about my mother over the years lies?

07:42.960 --> 07:44.160
My mother was born
into a high-ranking family

07:44.760 --> 07:46.520
and was skilled in all the refined arts.

07:46.600 --> 07:49.320
From small seal script,
painting, to the guqin.

07:49.400 --> 07:50.440
Can you do any of that?

07:50.520 --> 07:51.520
If you were my mother,

07:51.600 --> 07:52.880
you'd know how to write in that script.

07:52.960 --> 07:55.680
Show me. Do it!

07:56.280 --> 07:57.240
You cannot!

07:57.840 --> 07:59.760
Your hands are fit for nothing
but wielding blades and spears.

07:59.840 --> 08:01.600
You know nothing but killing!

08:01.680 --> 08:03.640
Your hands are soaked in blood!
You are not my mother!

08:03.720 --> 08:05.320
She is nothing like you!

08:06.280 --> 08:08.600
-Zhao.
-Let her finish.

08:09.560 --> 08:10.640
My mother…

08:13.200 --> 08:14.720
had delicate brows

08:15.720 --> 08:16.840
and skin like porcelain.

08:17.480 --> 08:21.360
She is the kindest mother in the world.

08:22.080 --> 08:23.440
My mother,

08:24.680 --> 08:26.320
even in death,

08:27.160 --> 08:28.280
would never abandon me.

08:28.360 --> 08:30.040
If she were still alive,

08:31.560 --> 08:34.880
she would never deceive me.

08:36.120 --> 08:38.520
Do you think you're worthy?

08:41.039 --> 08:43.159
-Zhao.
-Did I say anything wrong?

08:43.760 --> 08:46.200
Is this not what you told me, Father?

08:46.280 --> 08:48.800
My mother was a noble lady
from the Capital who died of illness.

08:48.880 --> 08:51.480
You told me every single bit of this.

08:51.560 --> 08:52.600
Or have all of these been lies

08:52.680 --> 08:54.680
you fabricated over all these years?

08:55.400 --> 08:56.440
What is real, exactly?

08:57.240 --> 08:59.080
The mother you spoke of is fake,

08:59.160 --> 09:00.520
and you hid your critical illness from me.

09:00.600 --> 09:01.560
What in the world is real?

09:01.640 --> 09:02.680
Enough!

09:04.880 --> 09:05.960
You are right.

09:06.960 --> 09:07.880
I am not your mother.

09:09.600 --> 09:13.240
The General is too ill to distinguish

09:14.000 --> 09:15.280
between stories and reality.

09:15.360 --> 09:17.560
Since my father is talking nonsense,

09:18.080 --> 09:21.120
take this worthless piece of junk
that nobody wants

09:21.200 --> 09:22.400
and leave my house.

09:23.320 --> 09:24.560
JOY AND HEALTH FOREVER

09:41.040 --> 09:42.240
Why…

09:43.440 --> 09:45.040
would you say that?

09:48.040 --> 09:49.120
She is

09:50.880 --> 09:52.880
not only your daughter,

09:54.120 --> 09:56.040
but also the Grand Princess
of the State of Chu.

09:57.720 --> 10:00.000
Her mother couldn't be
from the Northern Desert.

10:04.640 --> 10:05.920
And it should not be me.

10:08.160 --> 10:09.240
Alan.

10:54.640 --> 10:57.400
What right does she have to decide
how I should live my life?

10:58.320 --> 11:01.120
Perhaps she only wanted to keep you safe.

11:02.520 --> 11:03.640
Safe?

11:05.480 --> 11:07.120
For 19 years,

11:08.640 --> 11:09.880
I have spent every single day
yearning for my mother,

11:09.960 --> 11:11.240
who I thought was dead.

11:12.400 --> 11:13.880
Now I realize

11:16.160 --> 11:19.840
the cruelest irony
isn't that I wept over an empty grave,

11:21.040 --> 11:22.560
but that she chose

11:25.000 --> 11:27.200
to cast me aside from the very beginning.

11:30.920 --> 11:32.200
When someone truly does not care,

11:34.400 --> 11:36.000
they do not even bother to lie.

11:37.760 --> 11:38.960
When I was eight,

11:40.440 --> 11:42.280
my mother sent me back to the Xie Family

11:43.160 --> 11:44.440
with a promise

11:45.160 --> 11:46.720
that she would return for me,

11:47.560 --> 11:48.760
yet

11:49.960 --> 11:51.360
she never did.

11:52.120 --> 11:53.560
Are you trying to tell me

11:54.480 --> 11:55.760
that their lies

11:57.040 --> 11:58.000
were an act of love?

11:58.800 --> 12:00.160
Lies come in many forms.

12:02.320 --> 12:04.240
Some deceive to inflict pain,

12:05.240 --> 12:06.840
while others hide the truth

12:08.880 --> 12:10.040
to protect.

12:14.880 --> 12:16.880
But I deserve the truth,

12:16.960 --> 12:18.880
and I don't want protection built on lies.

12:19.880 --> 12:21.120
And I have no desire

12:22.400 --> 12:25.120
to remain a fragile soul,
forever shielded from reality.

12:26.400 --> 12:28.040
Nineteen years.

12:31.160 --> 12:32.880
They kept me in the dark for 19 years.

12:39.000 --> 12:41.200
Now that the truth is out,
what do you plan to do?

12:42.560 --> 12:44.560
Will you stay here demanding answers,

12:45.640 --> 12:46.960
or will you return

12:47.680 --> 12:49.600
to your father,
who has so little time left?

12:54.360 --> 12:55.240
Zhao,

12:57.200 --> 13:00.200
trust is not for debating right and wrong.

13:06.840 --> 13:08.920
The General is fading away.

13:10.360 --> 13:12.720
Do you really want to waste
these final moments placing blame?

13:14.920 --> 13:16.160
-But--
-There are no buts.

13:16.240 --> 13:18.040
You've missed 19 years.

13:18.840 --> 13:20.280
Do you really want

13:20.960 --> 13:22.400
to let these last moments
become another regret?

13:36.520 --> 13:39.040
Uncle, are you feeling any better?

13:40.640 --> 13:43.720
It warms my heart to see you
so concerned for me, Yu.

13:44.560 --> 13:45.840
I will be well again very soon.

13:49.080 --> 13:49.920
Your Majesty,

13:50.880 --> 13:52.440
Deng Yi has approved the frontier memorial

13:52.520 --> 13:54.840
and has dispatched riders posthaste
to Yunzhong Prefecture.

13:59.520 --> 14:01.960
Mr. Deng never fails to deliver.

14:10.640 --> 14:13.800
Yu, do you know the parable

14:13.880 --> 14:16.760
of turning a man's own weapon against him?

14:19.280 --> 14:22.080
No matter. I shall teach you.

14:30.960 --> 14:32.480
You two, to that position.

14:33.000 --> 14:34.320
The two of you, guard that sector.

14:34.400 --> 14:35.600
Stay alert.

14:42.160 --> 14:44.160
I heard the court
has approved your rewards.

14:44.240 --> 14:47.080
You'll soon be heading
to the frontier to take up your post.

14:47.720 --> 14:49.760
-I'll set out tomorrow.
-Wonderful.

14:49.840 --> 14:51.680
Whether your clan
can restore its former glory

14:51.760 --> 14:53.000
depends on the feats you accomplish.

14:53.640 --> 14:55.840
This success was merely
a stroke of fortune.

14:55.920 --> 14:57.240
Fortune?

14:58.320 --> 15:00.000
We were disgraced and out of favor.

15:00.080 --> 15:01.520
Promotion and reward were never certain.

15:02.240 --> 15:03.800
Fortunately, a benefactor
lent their support,

15:04.320 --> 15:07.400
and given the shifting tides of the court,
it was finally approved.

15:07.480 --> 15:08.440
A benefactor?

15:11.920 --> 15:14.600
Anyone who helps my family rise again
is a benefactor to me.

15:16.000 --> 15:21.400
I heard the reward list
was issued by the Grand Princess.

15:25.240 --> 15:28.320
She is, indeed, no ordinary woman.

15:47.440 --> 15:48.720
Apply some ointment for that burn.

15:48.800 --> 15:51.280
Father loves to eat my jujube cake,

15:52.160 --> 15:53.160
so I must finish making it.

16:01.600 --> 16:02.760
It is hard to mix this filling
with chopsticks.

16:03.840 --> 16:04.840
Try using this instead.

17:43.040 --> 17:46.440
You and the General loved each other
yet were forced apart.

17:47.240 --> 17:48.200
Why refuse to admit it?

17:49.080 --> 17:50.280
We did love each other.

17:51.600 --> 17:52.640
But Zhao

17:53.680 --> 17:55.640
cannot have a mother
from the Northern Desert,

17:56.840 --> 17:58.120
just as Chu Ling

18:00.200 --> 18:02.320
cannot have a wife of such origin.

18:04.960 --> 18:09.120
If you truly care for them,
ask no more of this.

18:26.400 --> 18:27.880
May I ask you a question?

18:31.800 --> 18:33.200
Have you ever had regrets?

18:33.280 --> 18:34.400
About what?

18:35.040 --> 18:36.680
Leaving her

18:37.840 --> 18:39.840
and letting her believe she had no mother

18:41.320 --> 18:42.920
and growing up burdened by that sorrow.

18:47.080 --> 18:48.280
Some things

18:50.280 --> 18:52.440
-cannot be changed by regret alone.
-But what about now?

18:53.040 --> 18:57.840
She is inside, shattered and inconsolable.

18:59.320 --> 19:00.360
Can you really bear to see her like this?

19:04.400 --> 19:05.560
What can I do?

19:08.120 --> 19:09.640
Should I acknowledge who I am

19:12.120 --> 19:14.360
and force her to bear
the shame of enemy blood,

19:14.440 --> 19:16.000
or should I strip her

19:17.800 --> 19:19.440
of honor

19:20.760 --> 19:22.520
and plunge her into infamy?

19:31.920 --> 19:32.920
This hairpin was meant

19:34.000 --> 19:35.920
for her coming of age.

19:36.000 --> 19:37.360
I can see

19:38.560 --> 19:39.920
that you truly cared for her,

19:40.520 --> 19:41.720
so please give it to her.

19:44.440 --> 19:45.720
Do not tell her it came from me.

19:46.880 --> 19:47.920
Just say

19:49.560 --> 19:52.440
that it is a gift from you.

20:21.000 --> 20:23.560
They are merely desperate fugitives,

20:23.640 --> 20:25.360
so what is there to fear?

20:26.880 --> 20:29.720
I only worry that they harbor resentment
over Wangcheng

20:29.800 --> 20:31.800
and refuse to cooperate
with us any longer.

20:34.920 --> 20:35.960
Wangcheng?

20:36.040 --> 20:40.160
What does that have to do with us?

20:41.920 --> 20:44.520
The slaughter of those remnants
of the Northern Desert

20:45.200 --> 20:46.800
was entirely Chu Zhao's doing, was it not?

20:47.600 --> 20:50.160
-Indeed, Your Highness.
-Speaking of the Northern Desert,

20:51.240 --> 20:53.480
I have another matter to ask you about.

21:01.000 --> 21:02.880
I told you

21:03.480 --> 21:05.040
goods logged under the stables

21:05.120 --> 21:07.600
must never bear
the Xiaonan Prefecture insignia again.

21:08.280 --> 21:09.680
This is my transgression.

21:09.760 --> 21:12.840
Those goods were meant to take
the northern official road.

21:12.920 --> 21:15.120
I only thought a hidden mark
would make it easier to identify.

21:15.720 --> 21:18.000
The fire at Wei Village five years ago

21:18.560 --> 21:20.600
wasn't enough of a lesson for you.

21:20.680 --> 21:24.360
How dare you put transport markings
on the goods again?

21:24.960 --> 21:26.200
I'll handle it immediately.

21:29.720 --> 21:30.840
Have you found

21:31.760 --> 21:33.960
the boy from Wei Village named Xiang?

21:35.000 --> 21:37.560
Your Highness, not yet.

21:44.640 --> 21:46.640
Please check on my father.

21:47.240 --> 21:48.400
Please save him. Hurry.

21:48.480 --> 21:49.920
No need.

21:50.760 --> 21:52.320
Zhao, stay.

21:53.200 --> 21:55.400
I have a few words for you.

21:57.000 --> 21:58.880
Father. I am here.

22:05.680 --> 22:07.080
Zhao.

22:07.760 --> 22:10.000
Do not resent your mother.

22:10.760 --> 22:12.600
Being born in the Northern Desert

22:13.360 --> 22:15.400
was not her fault.

22:16.280 --> 22:18.160
Trying to protect you

22:20.440 --> 22:21.800
is no reason for you

22:22.960 --> 22:25.040
to hate her either.

22:26.400 --> 22:28.160
Back then, she had nowhere else to turn.

22:29.440 --> 22:30.920
Leaving you

22:32.920 --> 22:36.120
was the only way to keep you safe.

22:37.280 --> 22:39.280
Your mother is a good woman.

22:39.920 --> 22:41.640
And she loves you very much.

22:42.880 --> 22:45.040
The fault is mine…

22:46.280 --> 22:48.480
and the fault of these troubled times,

22:49.640 --> 22:51.600
which robbed her of the chance

22:52.200 --> 22:54.920
to watch you grow.

23:00.320 --> 23:03.600
Alan, come here.

23:05.200 --> 23:06.240
Father.

23:07.320 --> 23:08.840
Zhao,

23:08.920 --> 23:12.080
I do not have much time left.

23:12.880 --> 23:15.160
I ask for nothing more

23:16.160 --> 23:18.200
than the chance to bid your mother

23:19.520 --> 23:21.520
a proper farewell.

23:59.360 --> 24:02.240
When we parted all those years ago,

24:03.040 --> 24:04.040
we swore

24:04.960 --> 24:07.120
we'd never meet again.

24:08.080 --> 24:09.720
Now death draws near,

24:11.360 --> 24:12.960
and truly,

24:15.720 --> 24:17.320
we never shall.

24:45.480 --> 24:47.720
They call me

24:49.120 --> 24:51.320
the God of War,

24:55.800 --> 24:57.800
but without the woman I loved,

24:59.640 --> 25:01.640
I have been nothing more

25:03.680 --> 25:07.280
than a hollow shell for 19 years.

25:13.560 --> 25:14.520
Alan.

25:15.040 --> 25:17.920
Yes. I'm here.

26:04.640 --> 26:08.960
MIGHT AND RIGHT

26:56.880 --> 26:58.400
<i>The Xie Family's crest?</i>

27:08.320 --> 27:09.160
Someone.

27:10.720 --> 27:11.560
Yes.

27:11.640 --> 27:14.000
Take this to the Army Physician
for examination.

27:14.080 --> 27:15.240
Yes.

27:20.520 --> 27:22.960
VALIANT GUARDIANS OF THE LAND

27:34.720 --> 27:36.720
Your Highness,
I have examined this medicine.

27:36.800 --> 27:40.200
It is refined from several deadly poisons.

27:41.120 --> 27:44.200
For a short time, it can accelerate
the flow of qi and blood,

27:44.280 --> 27:45.720
greatly enhance
muscular and skeletal strength,

27:45.800 --> 27:48.400
and even give the dying
a final burst of vitality.

27:49.400 --> 27:52.240
It bears a striking resemblance
to a strange deadly poison

27:52.320 --> 27:54.520
recorded in ancient texts
called the Bloodburn Pill.

27:55.320 --> 27:56.600
When did my father take this medicine?

27:58.960 --> 28:01.560
I remember on the Double Ninth Festival
in the 16th year of Tianshu,

28:01.640 --> 28:03.240
the General was struck by a poisoned arrow

28:03.840 --> 28:05.320
and was on the brink of death.

28:05.400 --> 28:06.680
He took a pill

28:06.760 --> 28:08.840
that wasn't part of the army's supplies.

28:09.440 --> 28:10.600
Wasn't it examined at the time?

28:10.680 --> 28:13.080
It was an emergency and there was no time.

28:13.160 --> 28:15.880
And after he took it,
nothing seemed amiss.

28:15.960 --> 28:17.800
So it was not investigated further

28:17.880 --> 28:19.400
and was only briefly recorded
in the files.

28:20.720 --> 28:23.720
No wonder the General's health
has been declining.

28:23.800 --> 28:27.880
This is not a life-saving medicine
but a death warrant.

28:28.680 --> 28:31.520
After one takes it,
toxins accumulate within the body,

28:31.600 --> 28:33.440
gradually eroding the heart
in an irreversible way.

28:34.240 --> 28:36.760
Ancient records state
that once this medicine is consumed,

28:36.840 --> 28:38.680
a second pill must be taken
three years later

28:38.760 --> 28:39.880
in order to extend life
by another three years.

28:40.640 --> 28:42.320
If the follow-up pill
is not taken in time,

28:42.400 --> 28:44.880
the body will undergo rapid decline

28:44.960 --> 28:46.840
beyond any possibility of recovery.

28:49.760 --> 28:50.960
You just said

28:51.800 --> 28:54.040
that wasn't part of the army's supplies.

28:54.680 --> 28:56.200
Then where did it come from?

28:58.920 --> 28:59.920
Speak.

29:01.400 --> 29:02.360
It was given…

29:04.760 --> 29:05.600
by Jiu.

29:07.920 --> 29:09.160
<i>In my past life,</i>

29:09.240 --> 29:10.360
<i>when the Anping Rebellion broke out</i>

29:10.440 --> 29:12.120
<i>on the eighth day of the eighth month,</i>
<i>in the 19th year of Tianshu,</i>

29:12.200 --> 29:14.240
<i>Jiu delivered me to Xiao Xun</i>

29:14.320 --> 29:15.880
<i>and rode straight back</i>
<i>to Yunzhong Prefecture.</i>

29:16.600 --> 29:19.280
<i>In other words,</i>
<i>if he provided the medicine,</i>

29:19.880 --> 29:22.120
<i>Father would have taken the second pill</i>
<i>in time for the Double Ninth Festival,</i>

29:22.200 --> 29:23.560
<i>granting him three more years.</i>

29:23.640 --> 29:25.280
<i>Only to have the poison manifest</i>
<i>in the third year of Anping.</i>

29:26.520 --> 29:28.200
<i>But in this life,</i>

29:28.280 --> 29:29.760
<i>in the 19th year of Tianshu,</i>

29:29.840 --> 29:32.760
<i>the wedding was called off,</i>
<i>the Anping Rebellion came early,</i>

29:32.840 --> 29:33.760
<i>and because of me,</i>

29:33.840 --> 29:35.000
<i>Xie Yanlai was appointed</i>
<i>Imperial Guard Commander,</i>

29:35.080 --> 29:36.600
<i>detaining him long in the Capital,</i>

29:36.680 --> 29:38.680
<i>making him miss the time</i>
<i>to give Father the pill.</i>

29:38.760 --> 29:40.960
<i>That is why Father</i>
<i>succumbed to the poison.</i>

29:41.040 --> 29:43.560
<i>Thus, the only one</i>
<i>who could have given him the medicine</i>

29:43.640 --> 29:45.080
<i>is Xie Yanlai.</i>

30:10.400 --> 30:12.320
Did you give this to my father?

30:19.560 --> 30:20.480
Yes.

30:21.480 --> 30:25.840
The Army Physician said
this is a drastic drug that saves a life

30:26.640 --> 30:27.880
only to end it later.

30:28.640 --> 30:31.560
-What did you say?
-I'm asking you…

30:32.640 --> 30:36.720
what your true intentions were
when you gave my father poison.

30:40.320 --> 30:41.280
<i>Yanlai.</i>

30:42.280 --> 30:43.760
This secret medicine, accessible

30:43.840 --> 30:45.240
only to the direct lineage
of the Xie clan,

30:46.120 --> 30:47.600
has the efficacy to revive the dying.

30:48.320 --> 30:49.280
Keep it with you,

30:50.080 --> 30:51.680
just in case.

31:00.200 --> 31:01.080
The pills.

31:03.920 --> 31:05.080
You lied to me.

31:11.160 --> 31:12.000
Yes,

31:14.760 --> 31:16.120
I gave the General the pills.

31:18.480 --> 31:20.200
If you want revenge,

31:24.520 --> 31:26.360
you can take my life right now.

31:27.600 --> 31:29.880
Is this your only explanation?

31:36.080 --> 31:37.120
Xie Yanlai,

31:40.760 --> 31:42.720
do you honestly think I won't kill you?

32:22.120 --> 32:23.240
Do it.

34:24.840 --> 34:25.880
Why?

34:33.840 --> 34:35.360
You claimed you owed me.

34:44.120 --> 34:45.199
Now…

34:49.080 --> 34:50.920
we are square.
